node.detail_zh: 患者過往健康良好，2 月 5 日至 6 月 27 曾到印度，返港後由檢疫中心送院，沒有病徵，與第 #1200 宗個案患者有關連。
node.detail_en: The patient has good past health and was in India between Feb 5 and June 27. She was transferred to hospital from the quarantine centre. She has no symptoms. Her case is epidemiologically linked to the case of patient #1200.
